{"tid":1378480,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"我二次創作左一個屬於香港人既標誌想整成襟針","createTime":"2019-07-28T15:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T18:57:59.000Z","uid":282718,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"33aa8f080ca6c35d1986d8f1649185eba82daf27","tid":1378480,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"我二次創作左一個屬於香港人既<br />\n飢餓遊戲 Mockingjay 學舌鳥既標誌，想整成襟針<br />\n如果有睇呢套戲既人應該會知<br />\n呢套戲係講反抗一個用極權去重建國家威嚴既政府<br />\n市民追求自由既一套電影<br />\n從一開始無人敢反抗，到有少數人表態<br />\n到後來大家團結起黎一齊推翻極權<br />\n唔好放棄 堅持到底 總有機會<br />\n極權主義最怕既 就係唔聽話既人民<br />\n我好欣賞戲中既精神 其中既三指手勢都好有意思<br />\n有興趣可以去重溫一下<br />\n<br />\n講返正題 我想將呢個標誌整做襟針<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我無咁多銀兩 所以想籌集下資金<br />\n又或者如果夠多資金 可以整多啲<br />\n如果有人夾左 可以好似夾訂咁 <br />\n你夾左幾錢就比返幾多成品你 一蚊都唔會收多 <br />\n當然如果你只想捐助 都可以<br />\n<br />\nBtw 如果覺得幅圖柒既 唔好屌 怕痛<br />\n始終唔係專業人士 望見諒 可以比下意見<br />\n如果有興趣既 可以tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Iu3IrBOW0fu5h6lGEO2-fQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FIu3IrBOW0fu5h6lGEO2-fQ&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=fb0c33e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Iu3IrBOW0fu5h6lGEO2-fQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90wNPgL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90wNPgL.jpg&h=7c8f0516&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CO4r4Qa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCO4r4Qa.jpg&h=5b8a1377&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xy7QM3z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxy7QM3z.jpg&h=29004ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIf you think for one second that the Capital will ever treat us fairly, you are lying to yourselves.<br />\nBecause we know who they are and what they do. <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>We must fight back. </strong></span></span><br />\nYou can torture us and bomb us and burn our districts to the ground. <br />\nDo you see that? Fire is catching.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">If we burn, you burn with us.</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"502283578af7334b669dd1baf6b35cc75c1312dd","tid":1378480,"uid":52703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"有心，但係有進步空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723015f0aa0a35d0d2363e35a9d24306f53f96d1","tid":1378480,"uid":263464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:03:04.000Z","msg":"(728)(TVB)警察使用燃燒彈，並誤中記者！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/angus.lau.963/videos/2083448135094256/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fangus.lau.963%2Fvideos%2F2083448135094256%2F&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=ab3879d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/angus.lau.963/videos/2083448135094256/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/lcz2l1cp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Flcz2l1cp&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=33f136ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/lcz2l1cp</a><br />\n(728)警察特登用盾牌推跌老人家<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/alice.ng.0906/videos/10156315649091471/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Falice.ng.0906%2Fvideos%2F10156315649091471%2F&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=827da042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/alice.ng.0906/videos/10156315649091471/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/qlq5sd7z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fqlq5sd7z&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=b2633d95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/qlq5sd7z</a><br />\n(728)(HKUSU)橋上警員向地上的警員施放催淚彈。<br />